title: MAGNETO 0 (1993 one-shot) (Marvel) REQUESTED Claremont Bolton
description:
BIll Sienkiewicz cover. Reprints Classic X-Men 12 & 19 backup stories by Chris Claremont and John Bolton. Pin-ups by John Byrne/Terry Austin, Steve Epting/Tom Palmer, and Greg Capullo/Kevin Conrad.

All credit goes to the original scanner and to PeteThePIPster, whose Complete Marvel Chronology project is an uncanny resource for all of us looking for an obscure back issue or 2.

Please seed and share.  --STF
